	abstract = {We establish an impossibility result for New Keynesian models with a frictionless labor market: these models cannot simultaneously match plausible estimates of marginal propensities to consume (MPCs), marginal propensities to earn (MPEs), and ﬁscal multipliers. A HANK model with sticky wages provides a solution to this trilemma.},
